{"tid":1142862,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"木村光希模特兒出道一年 巴黎行天橋被日本網民嘲笑指未夠班","createTime":"2019-05-07T11:03:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T12:52:39.000Z","uid":9573,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"811ce49abe915f787d85992b057c79e3181646d4","tid":1142862,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:03:28.000Z","msg":"日本天王木村拓哉與妻子工藤靜香的二女兒木村光希（Koki），以模特兒身分出道1周年，去年出道時就因為木村女兒的身分之前全亞洲矚目。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/05/20190504-EN-%E6%9C%A8%E6%9D%91%E5%85%89%E5%B8%8C1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F05%2F20190504-EN-%25E6%259C%25A8%25E6%259D%2591%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%25B8%258C1.jpg&h=25e2827c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKoki首次登上國際舞台，到巴黎為大品牌行天橋。<br />\n<br />\n不過，Koki一直被指是靠父母的庇蔭下才會如此矚目，昨日她更有機會走上時裝大舞台，到巴黎為國際品牌的「2020早春度假系列」行天橋，她自己亦十分之興奮，在其社交網以英文留言，感謝大會給她這個機會，又指自己是夢想成真。不過，只得16歲的她卻被日本網民狂嘲笑，指她走在國際時裝舞台仍未夠班。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/04/20190414-EN-%E6%9C%A8%E6%9D%91%E5%85%89%E5%B8%8C1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F04%2F20190414-EN-%25E6%259C%25A8%25E6%259D%2591%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%25B8%258C1.jpg&h=212a678d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2018/11/20181127_EN_%E6%9C%A8%E6%9D%91%E5%85%89%E5%B8%8C04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2018%2F11%2F20181127_EN_%25E6%259C%25A8%25E6%259D%2591%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%25B8%258C04.jpg&h=62dce59b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n木村光希。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/05/20190504-EN-%E6%9C%A8%E6%9D%91%E5%85%89%E5%B8%8C2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F05%2F20190504-EN-%25E6%259C%25A8%25E6%259D%2591%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%25B8%258C2.jpg&h=ab6d859f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKoki行天橋時明顯見到身材稍遜於其他模特兒。<br />\n<br />\n日本網民看過Koki在社交網上載了行天橋的片段，指她明顯身高比起其餘模特兒矮了一截，身形、步伐等，仍與國際模特兒差一大截距離。有網民指，Koki現時只得16歲，其母親不聽意見，太心急將女兒捧上位，令她成為被嘲笑的對象，對於仍是少女的Koki反而會帶來壞影響。當日的時裝騷有眾多國際名人在場，包括名模歌地亞雪花（Claudia Schiffer）、法國女星Vanessa Paradis及其女兒Lily-Rose，周杰倫與老婆昆凌亦是座上客。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9f9zDoB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9f9zDoB.jpg&h=14162072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n木村光希被日本網民狂嘲笑。"},{"pid":"e46bdcbfc176e728009e2a17c6c896ba3d91509f","tid":1142862,"uid":113373,"like":16,"dislike":6,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:04:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">反對修訂逃犯條例 香港的終局之戰</span><br />\n<br />\n星期六 早上9點 <br />\n立法會將會開會討論有關修訂 暫未知會否表決 <br />\n由於秘書處政變 原本由涂謹申主持會議改為石禮謙主持<br />\n<br />\n事態危急<br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 無需證據 無需理由<br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條&gt;&gt;&gt;(需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 &gt;&gt;&gt;(莫需有，中國政府可任意控告香港人任何罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由)</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"4478ee8bd5d396bf4aeea5db34900b50f6e828e5","tid":1142862,"uid":86928,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:07:29.000Z","msg":"人地16歲行chanel<br />\n幾多人再靚再高身材再好 呢件事都極遙不可及<br />\n所以識再多野都不及識投胎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6fe8025fcc8823ffaa15ff0802f9a8271c7998","tid":1142862,"uid":213877,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:07:47.000Z","msg":"佢老豆係邊個？呢D咪就係父幹囉<br />\n你理撚得佢夠唔夠班呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla